author: max
name: EmbedUptime
install_msg:
Thanks for installing. Once you load this cog, it will replace the uptime in core with this one, on unload you will have the core one back.
You can toggle replies off by using `[p]uptimeset`.
Feel free to check out the docs for this cog <https://maxbooiii.gitbook.io/maxcogs/cogs/embeduptime>
description: Shows current uptime of the bot.
short: Shows current uptime of the bot.
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not store any End User Data.
